misc: Rarely uses his driver, which has raised questions about his masculinity.
biography: Ossi, a competitor known for his strategic approach and thoughtful demeanor, is a familiar face at the Hector Trophée, representing the esteemed Kullo Golf Club.

While his skills with irons and putting are widely admired, Ossi's reluctance to unleash the driver has sparked considerable debate among fans and analysts alike. Some have even gone as far as questioning his masculinity, a topic that Ossi usually brushes aside with a polite, yet firm, smile.

Having participated in the Hector Trophée twice before, Ossi is eager to leverage his course knowledge and refine his tactics for the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, where he will make his third appearance.
